📧🤖 Week-5 | Final Project – Automated Email Classifier in n8n

In this project, we will build an **automated email classification system** using **n8n workflows**.

The system will:

✔ Read incoming emails
✔ Classify them using AI
✔ Route them to the correct category
✔ Take automated actions

Example categories:

* Support
* Sales
* Billing
* Spam

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

📌 1. Project Goal

Automate email management by:

* Identifying email intent
* Categorizing emails automatically
* Triggering appropriate workflows

Example:

```text
Email: "I need help resetting my password."
↓
Category: Support
↓
Create support ticket
```

